<DigiLayout lang="en" title="About us" description="What DigiClara is and how its editorial team works.">
  <section class="section"><div class="page-shell article-body">
    <p class="eyebrow">About DigiClara</p>
    <h1>Clarity, independence and practical technology</h1>
    <p>DigiClara is an independent blog with guides, comparisons, and resources to choose software, protect devices, and improve digital privacy.</p>
    <h2>Mission</h2><p>We explain everyday technology with clear language, without absolute promises or commercial pressure.</p>
    <h2>Editorial independence</h2><p>Conclusions are based on public documentation, explained criteria and practical tests only when they were actually performed. Future commercial relationships must be identified.</p>
    <h2>Updates and sources</h2><p>We review content when systems, policies or recommendations change. If information is missing, we prefer to say so rather than invent it.</p>
  </div></section>
</DigiLayout>
